headline: Boeing, United, American Airlines stocks react to Air India crash
summary: Yahoo Finance host Brad Smith tracks today's top moving stocks and biggest market stories in this Market Minute, including Boeing's (BA) negative stock reaction to the Air India crash that killed 242 people, as well as the stock moves from United Airlines (UAL) and American Airlines (AAL); both airways also fly the Boeing 787 Dreamliner. Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.
